  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt; 55 years of age,

          -  Subfoveal occult only CNV due to AMD,

          -  &lt; 4 disc areas or &gt; 4 disc areas

          -  VA &lt; 0.4

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Sign of classic CNV,

          -  CNV in other diagnoses than AMD,
      </textblock>
